If you do not already know the greatest irony for Singapore out of this CV19 pandemic is that in 2020/2021, Singapore will see the biggest spike in the number of babies born in these two years;

And the SG baby boom coincided with the period when Singaporeans are more relaxed, less distracted with the blink blink 'buzzing' entertainment economy prioritized by the LHL's administration and less stress-up in the SG rat-race, working from home;

And get this fact: LEAST number of foreigners and FTs allowed into Singapore during this CV19 period, never witnessed over the last 16 YEARS of the LHL's administration FT economic policy!
